import React from 'react'
import{Nav,NavbarContainer,NavLogo} from './Nav'
const Navbar = () => {
    return (
        <>
       <Nav>
         <NavbarContainer>
             <NavLogo>
              dolla
             </NavLogo>
         </NavbarContainer>
       </Nav>
       </>
    )
}

export default Navbar
